7cde3b8a2318,"what is the best way to travel the world? i'm thinking it's by plane because spending too long travelling would be terrible, what do you think?","Well, it depends on your preferences, budget, and where you want to travel.

Air travel is definitely fast and can cover long distances. It's time-efficient for those who're short on time and want to cover a lot of ground in a short period. But it can also be quite expensive!

