80c1303796e7,Think of a new way to market a pair of sneakers.,"One creative way to market a pair of sneakers could be through an interactive virtual reality experience. Customers could put on a virtual reality headset and be transported to a digital world where they can see, touch, and interact with the sneakers in a variety of scenarios. For example, they could test the sneakers in different environments such as hiking trails, city streets, or gym floors, and experience their comfort and performance firsthand.

