7ae748e6df8a,What are private military companies?,"Private military companies are companies that offer military services and sometimes security services, but are not formally part of any government’s military or security forces. Private military companies are generally hired by governments or organizations to provide services that are too dangerous or too costly for their own forces, such as close protection for high-profile individuals, security during natural disasters or complex peacekeeping operations."
