4962c5ee91ec,Could you provide me a few introductory phrases for the motivation behind singular value decomposition? I want to use them in the basics part of my thesis.,"Sure, here are a few possible introductory phrases you could use to explain the motivation behind Singular Value Decomposition (SVD) in your thesis:

