988f1a74af4c,"I've had 3 root canals in my right molar. The last one was more than 10 years ago. Lately, I've started to experience infections flaring up and my dentist says I have three options: to do another root canal, go for extraction and just eat anti-biotics every time there is an infection. How should I simplify this decision for me? What are the different factors to consider while making this decision?","It sounds like you're in a tough situation. I'm sorry to hear that you're having so much trouble with your tooth.

