3. Spider web decorations: Using cotton balls and black string, make a spider web in a corner of a room or on a door. Add a plastic spider for added spookiness.

4. Ghostly mason jars: Paint mason jars white and use black markers to draw ghostly faces. Put a battery-operated tea light inside for a glowing effect.

