[""United States Treasury Note/Bond"", ""1.2%"", ""22,120,821"", ""1,607,819"", ""5/15/27""]` -> ""data"" 
[""Total Unites States"", """", ""5,192,000""] -> ""total""
["""", """", """", """", ""5,029,331""] -> ""total""
[""201,199"", """", """", """", """"] -> ""total""


Please answer with a single word what each row is

